{"tid":1791271,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有店員受訪指：有黑警試圖抹走槍既指模，再放入發泡膠箱","createTime":"2019-12-20T16:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T17:31:01.000Z","uid":222970,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b6c84c5cbdaf0b2bc8e1c24feabf7fcce221227c","tid":1791271,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:06:40.000Z","msg":"2247 #大埔 #安慈路 #昌運中心 <br />\n附近餐廳有店員受訪，他指出當時聽到外面「呯」一聲巨響後就衝出店舖了解，看到一名青年被三個相信是便衣警察按在地上，其中一名持槍。有附近街坊喝止該持槍男子，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>他就把槍放在地上，並試圖抹走指模，該槍其後由相信是警察人士放入發泡膠箱</strong></span></span>。稍後有更多蒙面人士到達增援，其中一名身材高瘦的曾出示委任證，表明自己警察身份。<br />\n#蘋果 #立場"},{"pid":"b5d18c064375f8004e2569fd3c4bfc24c111913f","tid":1791271,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T16:12:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">12.22  愛丁堡<br />\n12.21  721五個月 <br />\n12.24 和你shop<br />\n12.24  夜晚尖咀見<br />\n12.31  和你拖<br />\n2020.1.1元旦大遊行</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sEffSro.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsEffSro.jpg&h=99a1f162&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VBcxEME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVBcxEME.jpg&h=7ab8f960&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKLvrrF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKLvrrF.jpg&h=653d2ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mY6iAj1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmY6iAj1.jpg&h=c159792d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tVOXym.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tVOXym.jpg&h=2b5d9c8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9uVGNZR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9uVGNZR.jpg&h=abdc3b7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fa930821587f9b0d9d7f946